markdownRemark.html:
A couple of years ago, I pushed a public site up using a beautiful Shopify template. Hundreds of dollars later, I’m back to something much more simple—and cheaper: github.io pages. The Gatsby Starter Blog template is a good place to start, with support for some of the tools I like to play around with.

In the meantime, here’s Bill Bailey reimagining The Doctor Who theme as Belgian jazz.

And if that’s too much of an insider joke, here’s an International Symphonic Mashup of The Kiffness - Alugalug Cat
